                    <span>This is heavenly music: I loved the sounds from the first track and can hardly wait to see the DVD. I have played the soundtrack for all eight hours of my work day today and still want to hear it again. <BR>I have been to the Far East and the music makes me want to return to see Nepal. I hope this region and people will not be devastated in the future.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Matches the splendor of the mountains</div>
